Famous by Kanye West.author: Kanye West
Famous by Kanye West.title: Famous by Kanye West
Famous by Kanye West.entry: The final game of the previous Rocket Lineup was disasterous, at best. The lineup was forsaken to fail with PJ Tucker suffering from a keen injury from a previous game and Harden being on a minutes restriction. The majority of the Rocket's offense depened on Russsell Westbrook. While he did score 46 of the Rocket's 104 points, he did so by shooting an abysmal 17 of 43 attempts, as well as going 2 of 9 from beyond the arc. His poor shot selection and questionale jumper continues to be a rising issue as the season progresses, especially in a system so dependendent on shooting as Mike D'Antoni's. The ball was in Westbrook's hands for most of the night, ultimately limiting the offensive capabilites and oppurtunities of the remaining roster.
